links: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n=0,...,1000
prog: (PARI) { default(realprecision, 10); t=(sqrt(5) + 1)/2; f=1/t; g=1/(1 + t); for (n=0, 1000, write("b060145.txt", n, " ", floor(n*f) - floor(n*g)); ) } [From _Harry J. Smith_, Jul 02 2009]
